 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing go is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person playing chess and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the chinese is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
